      "target": {
        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(sessions): prune stale gateway model-run sessions",
        "body": "## Summary\n- add a model-run-specific session retention setting with a conservative default of 24h\n- validate `session.maintenance.modelRunPruneAfter` in the strict session schema (`duration | number | false`)\n- prune stale `agent:*:explicit:model-run-<uuid>` probe sessions before global age/cap maintenance during write, load-time enforcement, and `sessions cleanup`\n- expose `modelRunPruned` / `prune-model-run` in cleanup summaries and dry-run plans\n\nFixes #88632\n\n## Real behavior proof\n\nBuilt the PR locally (`node scripts/build-all.mjs cliStartup`) and ran the real CLI against an isolated temp config/state/store:\n\n```console\n$ OPENCLAW_HOME=/tmp/openclaw-88632-proof/home \\\n  OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR=/tmp/openclaw-88632-proof/state \\\n  OPENCLAW_CONFIG_PATH=/tmp/openclaw-88632-proof/openclaw.json \\\n  node openclaw.mjs sessions cleanup --dry-run --json \\\n  --store /tmp/openclaw-88632-proof/sessions.json\n\n$ OPENCLAW_HOME=/tmp/openclaw-88632-proof/home \\\n  OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR=/tmp/openclaw-88632-proof/state \\\n  OPENCLAW_CONFIG_PATH=/tmp/openclaw-88632-proof/openclaw.json \\\n  node openclaw.mjs sessions cleanup --enforce --json \\\n  --store /tmp/openclaw-88632-proof/sessions.json\n```\n\nSynthetic redacted store contents before cleanup:\n\n```text\nagent:main:explicit:model-run-123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000  # stale model-run, 2d old\nagent:main:explicit:model-run-123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174001  # recent model-run\nagent:main:explicit:durable-control                                # durable control, 2d old\n```\n\nObserved summary:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"dryRun\": {\n    \"beforeCount\": 3,\n    \"afterCount\": 2,\n    \"modelRunPruned\": 1,\n    \"pruned\": 0,\n    \"capped\": 0,\n    \"wouldMutate\": true\n  },\n  \"enforce\": {\n    \"beforeCount\": 3,\n    \"afterCount\": 2,\n    \"modelRunPruned\": 1,\n    \"pruned\": 0,\n    \"capped\": 0,\n    \"wouldMutate\": true\n  },\n  \"remainingKeys\": [\n    \"agent:main:explicit:durable-control\",\n    \"agent:main:explicit:model-run-123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174001\"\n  ]\n}\n```\n\nThis shows the stale gateway model-run probe is reported/pruned, while the recent model-run and durable control session remain.\n\n## Testing\n- `node scripts/build-all.mjs cliStartup`\n- `pnpm tsgo:core:test`\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs run --config test/vitest/vitest.commands.config.ts src/commands/sessions-cleanup.test.ts`\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs run --config test/vitest/vitest.runtime-config.config.ts src/config/zod-schema.session-maintenance-extensions.test.ts src/config/sessions/store.pruning.test.ts src/config/sessions/store.pruning.integration.test.ts src/config/schema.help.quality.test.ts src/config/schema.base.generated.test.ts`\n- `pnpm exec oxfmt --check --threads=1 src/config/zod-schema.session.ts src/config/zod-schema.session-maintenance-extensions.test.ts src/commands/sessions-cleanup.test.ts src/commands/sessions-cleanup.ts src/config/schema.help.ts src/config/schema.labels.ts src/config/sessions/cleanup-service.ts src/config/sessions/runtime-types.ts src/config/sessions/store-load.ts src/config/sessions/store-maintenance.ts src/config/sessions/store.pruning.integration.test.ts src/config/sessions/store.pruning.test.ts src/config/sessions/store.ts src/config/types.base.ts`\n\nNote: full `pnpm format:check` still reports unrelated pre-existing formatting issues outside this PR's touched files.",
